\c 8
\s Ukukhonzwa kwezithombe ethempelini
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi ngomnyaka wesithupha, nge\add nyanga\add* yesithupha, ngolwesihlanu lwenyanga\x + 1.2.\x*, ngihlezi endlini yami, labadala bakoJuda behlezi phambi kwami\x + 11,12. 33.31. 7.26. 9.6. 14.1. 20.1,3. 2 Kho. 6.32. Jer. 19.1.\x*, isandla seNkosi uJehova sawa lapho phezu kwami\x + 1.3.\x*.
\v 2 Ngasengibona, khangela-ke, umfanekiso \add o\add*njengokubonakala komlilo\x + 1.27.\x*; kusukela ekubonakaleni kokhalo lwakhe kusiya phansi, umlilo; futhi kusukela kukhalo lwakhe kusiya phezulu\x + 1.27.\x* kunjengokubonakala kokukhazimula\x + Dan. 12.3.\x*, njengombala wethusi\x + 1.4.\x*.
\v 3 Waseselula\x + 2.9. Dan. 5.5.\x* isimo sesandla\x + 10.8.\x*, wangithatha ngesihluthu sekhanda lami\x + 8.36.\x*; uMoya wasengiphakamisela\x + 3.12.\x* phakathi komhlaba lamazulu\x + 2 Kor. 12.1-3.\x*, wangiletha eJerusalema emibonweni kaNkulunkulu, esivalweni sesango elingaphakathi, elikhangele ngenyakatho, lapho okwakulesihlalo\x + 5.11.\x* sesithombe sobukhwele\x + 8.5. Dute. 4.16.\x* esibanga ubukhwele.
\v 4 Khangela-ke, inkazimulo kaNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli\x + 1.28.\x* yayilapho, \add i\add*njengokubonakala engangikubone esihotsheni\x + 3.22.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Wasesithi kimi: Ndodana yomuntu, ake uphakamisele amehlo akho ngasendleleni yenyakatho. Ngasengiphakamisela amehlo ami ngasendleleni yenyakatho, khangela-ke, ngasenyakatho\x + Jer. 23.11.\x* kwesango lelathi\x + 8.16. 9.2. 40.47. Eks. 40.6,29.\x* kwakulalesisithombe sobukhwele entubeni.
\v 6 Wasesithi kimi: Ndodana yomuntu, uyakubona yini abakwenzayo, amanyala amakhulu\x + 7.20. Jer. 23.11.\x*\x + 8.17. 18.12.\x* ewenzayo indlu kaIsrayeli lapha, ukuze \add ngi\add*ye khatshana lendawo yami engcwele? Kodwa phenduka futhi, uzabona amanyala amakhulu kula\add la\add*.
\p
\v 7 Wasengisa emnyango weguma; lapho ngibona, njalo khangela, kwakulesikhala emdulini.
\v 8 Wasesithi kimi: Ndodana yomuntu, ake ugebhe emdulini. Ngathi ngigebha emdulini, khangela-ke kwakulomnyango.
\v 9 Wasesithi kimi: Ngena, ubone izinengiso ezimbi abazenzayo lapha.
\v 10 Ngasengingena, ngabona, khangela-ke, sonke isimo sokuhuquzelayo\x + Gen. 1.24. Roma 1.23.\x* lenyamazana ezinengekayo\x + 7.20. Jer. 23.11.\x* lazo zonke izithombe zendlu yakoIsrayeli, kubaziwe phezu komduli inhlangothi zonke ezizingelezeleyo\x + 16.26. 23.14. 4.1.16.26. Jobe 13.27.\x*.
\v 11 Futhi kwakumi phambi kwazo amadoda angamatshumi ayisikhombisa\x + Nani 11.16. Eks. 24.1.\x* akwabadala bendlu kaIsrayeli, loJahazaniya indodana kaShafani emi phakathi kwabo\x + Isa. 66.17.\x*\x + 2 Lan. 34.8.\x*; yileyo laleyo \add ilo\add*dengezi lwayo esandleni sayo, njalo iyezi eliqatha lempepha lenyuka.
\v 12 Wasesithi kimi: Ukubonile yini, ndodana yomuntu, lokho abadala bendlu kaIsrayeli\x + 8.1.\x* abakwenzayo emnyameni, ngulowo emakamelweni emifanekiso yakhe?\x + Zaga 25.11.\x* Ngoba bathi: IN\nd kosi\nd* kayisiboni\x + 9.9.\x*\x + Hlab. 10.11. Isa. 29.15. Jobe 22.13.\x*; iN\nd kosi\nd* iwutshiyile umhlaba\x + 9.9.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Wasesithi kimi: Phenduka futhi, uzabona izinengiso ezinkulu kakhulu abazenzayo.
\v 14 Wasengisa emnyango wesango lendlu yeN\nd kosi\x + 8.3.\x*\nd* eyayingasenyakatho; khangela-ke, kwakuhlezi abesifazana belilela uTamuzi.
\p
\v 15 Wasesithi kimi: Ubonile yini, ndodana yomuntu? Phenduka futhi, uzabona izinengiso ezinkulu kulalezi.
\v 16 Wasengingenisa egumeni lendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd* elingaphakathi\x + 10.3. 40.28. 43.5. 45.19. 46.1. 1 Kho. 6.36.\x*; khangela-ke, \add e\add*mnyango wethempeli leN\nd kosi\nd* phakathi\x + Jow. 2.17.\x* kwekhulusi\x + 1 Kho. 6.3.\x* lelathi\x + 8.5.\x* kwakulamadoda phose angaba ngamatshumi amabili lanhlanu\x + 11.1.\x*, imihlane yawo\x + Jer. 2.27. 32.33.\x* ingasethempelini leN\nd kosi\nd*, lobuso bawo bungasempumalanga; njalo bakhonza\x + Jer. 8.2.\x* ilanga ngasempumalanga\x + Jobe 31.26.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Wasesithi kimi: Ubonile yini, ndodana yomuntu? Kuyinto elula kundlu yakoJuda ukwenza izinengiso\x + 8.17. 18.12.\x* abazenzayo lapha yini? Ngoba bagcwalise ilizwe\x + 9.9.\x* ngobudlwangudlwangu\x + 7.23.\x*, baphendukele ukungithukuthelisa\x + Jer. 7.18.\x*; khangela-ke, bafaka ugatsha empumulweni yabo\x + 15.2.\x*.
\v 18 Ngakho lami ngizakwenza ngentukuthelo\x + 5.13.\x*; ilihlo lami kaliyikuhawukela, futhi kangiyikuyekela; lanxa bekhala endlebeni zami\x + Zaga 1.28.\x* ngelizwi elikhulu, kangiyikubezwa.
